切相关的商超、便利店、农贸市场、医疗机构正常营业，严格通风消杀、扫码测温，实施预约、错峰、限流措施。药店暂停销售发热类药品。 六、养老院、福利院、监所等机构暂停探视活动；公共浴室、美容美发、娱乐场所、线下培训、托幼机构等密闭场所暂停开放；公墓、骨灰堂（塔陵）暂停祭扫；宗教活动场所暂时关闭；餐饮场所严禁堂食；婚事暂缓、丧事简约。 七、严禁各类集聚性活动，非生活必需场所一律暂时停业。 本通告自发布之日起施行，并视疫情变化适时调整。郑州全市居民小区实行闭环管理，出租车网约车不得出市区运营"},"attached_info":"Cj8It/f/rYf0kf0sEAMaCDY4NDQ4NjE5IIjBs4gGMAM4kQNAE3IJNDc3NzU1MTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"313 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e08d92e7879e8fb3760f1e27ca2bd768.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1628251815.0049808","card_id":"Q_384087324","target":{"id":384087324,"title":"有哪些对视力伤害很大的行为？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/384087324","type":"question","created":1585656374,"answer_count":401,"follower_count":8964,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4793,32864,68816,93420],"comment_count":19,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8It/f/rYf0kf0sEAMaCDQ3NjMwNjkzILbkjPQFMBM4hEZAFHIJMzg0MDg3MzI0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"312 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0aed360bc82ea55594f1c3580df672be_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1628251815.0054526","card_id":"Q_476146837","target":{"id":476146837,"title":"为什么三体人不派两个水滴，一个封锁太阳，一个杀罗辑？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/476146837","type":"question","created":1627644431,"answer_count":40,"follower_count":148,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[72,3269,157063],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"三体第一舰队一共有十个水滴，三体人为什么不直接用两个水滴，一个封锁太阳，一个杀逻辑？仅仅是因为傲慢吗？以三体人几百万的发展过程来看，三体人是极度理智的物种，不应该存在傲慢的情绪？"},"attached_info":"Cj8It/f/rYf0kf0sEAMaCDY4MDkwNjQ4II/Ej4gGMAQ4lAF